data.description: Welcome Home! Craftsman Four bedroom, Three Bath Craftsman Open floor plan home with a three car garage on 1/2 acre in Holley By the Sea has ample room for a pool and just under 2900 sqft. Freshly painted and new carpet. Exceptional Kitchen with large island with breakfast nook, stainless appliances, granite countertops, and a large walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom has trey ceilings and oversized primary bathroom with a separate soaking tub, zero-entry all tiled walk in shower, and all bedrooms have walk-in closets. The backyard is fully fenced with room for a pool and has a covered lanai. Holley By the Sea offers community pools, gym, tennis, golf, pickleball, sound access, and bay access and so much more!! Within a few minutes drive to the Beach.
